	(text "IDRIVE: Mosfet Drive Current\n	Target: 200ns Rise, 100ns Fall\n	Gate-Drain Charge: 12nC\n		Rise: 12nC / 200ns = 60mA -> 75kΩ to AGND\n		Fall: 12nC / 100ns = 120mA -> 75kΩ to AGND\n\nMODE: PWM input mode\n	6-PWM -> Mode 0 -> tie to AGND\n\nGAIN: Current Sense Gain\n	40 V/V -> Tie to DVDD\n\nVDS: Overcurrent Protection\n	Max Current > 35A\n	RDSon@125°C = 3.5mΩ\n		Overcurrent Voltage = 35A * 3.5mΩ = 0.1225V\n		Choose 0.13V -> 18kΩ to AGND\n		Actual Overcurrent@125°C = 0.13V / 3.5mΩ ~ 37.14A"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 67.31 176.53 0)
		(effects
